| **crypto** | `modules.crypto` | Cryptographic hashing and HMACS |
| **ParseCSV** | `modules.ParseCSV` | Parse CSV strings to JSON arrays (async) |
| **ParseYML** | `modules.ParseYML` | Parse/stringify YAML (uses failsafe schema) |
